text: Diogo Ganchinho (born 12 September 1987) is a Portuguese trampoline gymnast. He represented Portugal at the 2008 Summer Olympics in Beijing, China and at the 2012 Summer Olympics in London, United Kingdom. In 2008, he finished in 11th place in the qualification round in the men's trampoline event. In 2012 he finished in 15th place in the qualification round in this event at the 2012 Summer Olympics. In 2009, he competed in the men's synchronized trampoline at the 2009 World Games held in Kaohsiung, Taiwan.
